<h2 id='patch-charity-details'>Patch Charity Details</h2>
<p>This endpoint can be used to update specific attributes of a charity.</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>http PATCH example.com/api/charities/<span class="o">{</span><span class="nb">id</span><span class="o">}</span>
</code></pre></div><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight javascript tab-javascript"><code><span class="nx">TODO</span>
</code></pre></div><h3 id='http-request'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>PATCH example.com/api/charities/2327833979673121796</code></p>
<h3 id='parameters'>Parameters</h3>
<p>Parameters can be any of the following:</p>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>name</td>
<td>The name of the charity</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>description</td>
<td>A longer description of the charity</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>about_us</td>
<td>An extra field to explain the purpose of the charity</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>street</td>
<td>The street number and name</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>suburb</td>
<td>The name of the suburb</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>city</td>
<td>The name of the city</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>province_id</td>
<td>The id from the list of provinces</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>email</td>
<td>The general email</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>telephone</td>
<td>The main telephone number</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>website</td>
<td>The website of the charity</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>registration_number</td>
<td>the NGO or similar (needs verification)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>gps_coords</td>
<td>Used for exact location</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>tags</td>
<td>A list of tag names use to categorise charities (fixed list)</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
